{"tw": {"4207080": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "愛的禮儀指導", "steam_appid": 4207080, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0390fd29737a2d50df6cf1c383de2c22.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0390fd29737a2d50df6cf1c383de2c22.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0390fd29737a2d50df6cf1c383de2c22.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>「這真是份好工作啊！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>恭喜你找到工作！你的工作是擔任某大企業的工作規則指導員！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">不曉得新職場的氣氛如何⋯⋯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">看來好像有點拘謹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你看了一下公司規則⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">長襪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">短髮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">腋下無毛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>白色內褲</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>胸部敏感</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>無性經驗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">咦？等等⋯⋯最後一項是⋯⋯？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0b4514c7986506cba8d15fc87e8f57f8.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0b4514c7986506cba8d15fc87e8f57f8.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0b4514c7986506cba8d15fc87e8f57f8.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>算了！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">不管公司規則有多怪，身為指導員的你也只能遵守。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">為了讓工作順利進行，你似乎也該和員工們打好「關係」⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/53126db9250f81edc6b60a4351d325e9.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/34e418cfe51d8b2f6233870f745adf29.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/34e418cfe51d8b2f6233870f745adf29.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/34e418cfe51d8b2f6233870f745adf29.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>開始上班前，員工會在走廊排成一列等待檢查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">請一一仔細確認他們有無違規。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">改變姿勢⋯⋯愛撫⋯⋯親吻⋯⋯脫衣⋯⋯手淫⋯⋯插入⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">為了查明真相，你必須不擇手段！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">滿意後再叫下一個員工進來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">工作內容很清楚明瞭吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/32b659998acad707aa4bd1971a1efb58.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/c6b50f4ca6c00c69a205ff3acdcea5cc.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/c6b50f4ca6c00c69a205ff3acdcea5cc.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/c6b50f4ca6c00c69a205ff3acdcea5cc.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">出現的員工皆為隨機形成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">從髮色、三圍、個性到家庭背景，皆為隨機設定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">依附障礙⋯⋯無性經驗⋯⋯害羞⋯⋯愛說謊⋯⋯總是獨自一人⋯⋯淫蕩⋯⋯雙性人⋯⋯抖Ｍ⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">會有各種類型的OL來到你的指導室！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">將角色加入「我的最愛」，就能進行特別指導！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/53d4dfa05faeb1664aa7d464e7fa44ed.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">確認員工的H資料時也能逐漸看到指導成果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">抽插次數⋯⋯高潮次數⋯⋯內射次數⋯⋯潮吹次數⋯⋯吞精次數⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">指導喜歡的員工，讓數字逐漸增加吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">好感度越高，說不定就能變得更親密⋯⋯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/4e9fd5c3afd8a8a3ac304c9b355fb8a7.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d95d9607defb0c54c9812d5e3a802cce.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d95d9607defb0c54c9812d5e3a802cce.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d95d9607defb0c54c9812d5e3a802cce.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">只要提升指導評價，就有機會外派到其他公司！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">外派地點說不定會有出乎意料的發展在等著你？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/ea52331ab69a8a9838f0ab23e3c78dde.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">用薪水買禮物送給員工吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">也能購買春藥或是能賦予特性（雙性人等）的藥物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">甚至也能買結婚戒指⋯⋯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">歡迎遊玩《愛的禮儀指導》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>本遊戲可控制H場景！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">每一關都有三個隨機形成的員工以及應遵守的公司規定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">發現違規時就用滑鼠點擊，糾正可疑的地方。指導次數越多越能提升「主導權」，可以深入探索員工不為人知的一面⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">只要評價和薪水增加，下一次的指導就會變得更加輕鬆。請一面尋找違規的地方，一面細細品嚐同事的肉體吧！要摸要上，由你決定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">不過要注意時間限制。壓力值超過100％時就會強制結束指導。請有技巧地糾正員工，別讓員工累積壓力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">商店裡的道具會隨著遊戲進行解鎖，讓你指導起來更加順利，獲得更舒適的遊玩體驗！提升好感度的禮物、讓員工瞬間發情的春藥、紓解壓力的道具、結婚戒指，甚至是讓員工生產的道具，令人血脈噴漲的道具一應俱全！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">此外，只要使用「引導力」獲得「指引化石」，就能隨心所欲賦予同事身體特殊的特性，如改變說話聲、雙性化、潮吹，甚至噴乳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">只要讓同事處女化，就能無數次享受對方重要的第一次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">遊戲共5關，數小時就能盡情體驗遊戲樂趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">破關後也能無限重玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">遊玩內容會被記錄至H資料內！將員工登錄至「我的最愛」，透過再次指導來提升好感度！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/5f863cce1926f6a0c52070a624606688.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/5f863cce1926f6a0c52070a624606688.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/5f863cce1926f6a0c52070a624606688.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d14ed90901f1a2cd2b5bf8e15be10d2f.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/