s://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/207d14e1cac7ab587ccc683204e14cbbb154710f/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776319525", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> 7/8/10/11</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}, "us": {"4207080": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "HR Department of Love", "steam_appid": 4207080, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/2d326d49290deba92c8e73e306e6de0a.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/2d326d49290deba92c8e73e306e6de0a.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/2d326d49290deba92c8e73e306e6de0a.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">&quot;Ahhh, what a wonderful job this is...&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Congratulations! You've been hired as manager of HR for an extremely successful corporation!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Just what does your new job entail, though?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Well, your new workplace is pretty strict. Company employees must adhere to the following rules:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Long socks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Short hair</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Shaved armpits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>White panties</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Sensitive breasts</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Virgin</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>...Wait, what were those last few?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0b4514c7986506cba8d15fc87e8f57f8.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0b4514c7986506cba8d15fc87e8f57f8.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/0b4514c7986506cba8d15fc87e8f57f8.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">That's right! Your new workplace's rules may be pretty bonkers, but you're the one who has to enforce them. And if you want to do your job well, you just might have to get a little intimate with your new coworkers...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d5d23e9defbd98b1456d6f16a29e54d2.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/34e418cfe51d8b2f6233870f745adf29.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/34e418cfe51d8b2f6233870f745adf29.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/34e418cfe51d8b2f6233870f745adf29.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">At the start of your shift, your coworkers will line up outside of your office, and you need to determine whether or not they're breaching company policy in any way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Change their position, feel them up, kiss them, strip them, finger them, fuck them...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Do whatever you need to do to ascertain the truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Once you're satisfied, send them on their way, and call the next person in... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Not too hard, is it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/5b5fc36e1868698b9dcb29cdc43fd8dd.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/c6b50f4ca6c00c69a205ff3acdcea5cc.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/c6b50f4ca6c00c69a205ff3acdcea5cc.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/c6b50f4ca6c00c69a205ff3acdcea5cc.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">All of your coworkers are completely randomly generated, so the possibilities are endless! You'll encounter all different kinds of hair colors, body types, cup sizes, personalities, and even backgrounds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Touch-starved... Virgin... Shy... Pathological liar... Lonely... Slut... Futanari... Masochist...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">All kinds of women will find themselves in your office!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You can even add coworkers to your favorites to call them back later for some... extra enforcing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/956f497f2b83c6e0544bd20bb8731da6.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Keep track of how your work is going with tons of different statistics attached to each of your coworkers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Times fucked... Times orgasmed... Times creampied... Times squirted... Loads swallowed...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Keep in touch with your favorite coworkers and get those numbers up! Over time, you'll be able to get more and more intimate with them...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/33671db8cd4457b1d22f19c5331a402c.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span>You've gotten so good at your job that other companies want to hire you, too! What kinds of possibilities await you at your new destinations?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d95d9607defb0c54c9812d5e3a802cce.poster.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d95d9607defb0c54c9812d5e3a802cce.webm?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/d95d9607defb0c54c9812d5e3a802cce.mp4?t=1776319525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4207080/extras/580d04471b29490109a2db2ac2123004.avif?t=1776319525\" width=756 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use the salary you get from your job to buy things for your coworkers! Presents will help you get along with them, but you can also buy different aphrodisiacs and medicines (some of which grant special characteristics, like becoming a futanari), or if you're ready for it, even a <i>wedding ring</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Become an HR manager today!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This game gives you the power to control your very own sex scenes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Each stage will give you three randomly generated coworkers to have fun with, as well as the company rules that they<i> should</i> be following!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">If they're breaking company policy in some way, select the corresponding area with your mouse and point it out! This will increase your &quot;Authority&quot; level, letting you access even more... private areas. Your rating as a manager will also go up, making future sessions even easier, and so will your salary! Try to find all the ways that your coworkers are breaking the rules, and enjoy yourself while you're at it! You can feel up, finger, and even fuck your coworkers all you like!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You don't have all the time in the world, though... If your coworker's stress meter fills up, she'll leave, so point out all her infringements before time runs out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">As you progress, you'll unlock items in the shop, making your job easier and more exciting! You can buy presents, which will make your coworkers like you more, aphrodisiacs, which will immediately get them hot and bothered, stress relieving items, wedding rings, and even an item that makes them give birth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The shop isn't the only place where you can change up your gameplay, though! Spend &quot;Authority Points&quot; to magically change your coworkers' bodies! You can give them dicks, make them squirt, lactate, and change their voices! You can even help them relive the most precious moments of their lives by giving them second virginities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Completing the main story and unlocking all 5 stages will take a few hours, but the fun doesn't stop there! You can replay any stage as many times as you like!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Everything you do will be recorded via stats, and you can add coworkers to your &quot;Favorites&quot; list to call them back 